      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "GRAND PERFECTION (1) flew the lids with a fast early split last time, hitting the frame with a 2 length second (22.54) over 395m at this track and making it two placings on end. Although beaten ran one of the quickest times on the card last start. Key chance in this line up. CARE FACTOR (2) finished second (22.26) two back at this track but out of the placings last time when 6th at Murray Bridge Straight. Strong form has emerged from his last run. Expected to give a good account. BREAKER OF RULES (5) has missed the frame at his last couple of starts but just a few runs back broke the clock when winning over 400m at Gawler, taking a Grade 3/4/5 in an exceptional 22.70. Expected to feature on best figures. BITTER FURY (7) gets a chance to improve on an unplaced run at his latest outing at this circuit.",
